{"type": "article", "id": 1370, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2014-07-07T08:25:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 1525, "name": "茶几"}, {"id": 1526, "name": "Duffy London"}, {"id": 1527, "name": "太阳能建筑"}, {"id": 1528, "name": "智能闹钟"}, {"id": 1529, "name": "玻璃灯具"}, {"id": 1530, "name": "Lanvin"}, {"id": 1531, "name": "帽子"}], "category": 17, "author": 1218, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052206171gGrqan6CpJhwUXy.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">1.  The Abyss Table by <a href=\"http://duffylondon.com/home-page/\" target=\"_blank\">Duffy London</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t这款名为“深渊”的茶几来自 Duffy London 工作室，利用多层的玻璃和木板搭建出戏剧般的海底深渊的效果，看下去仿佛看见了一张三维地质勘探图，让桌面拥有了充满神秘感的吸引力。<a href=\"http://duffylondon.com/home-page/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220608cPZgTKzhHMoay04e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220609j9TWEGXSNvyUgQFV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220609ROx47pL6sUPS1eQM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220610WJjyGVvkcT48m7A9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8234375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t2.  Floating Hawker by <a href=\"http://www.sparkarchitects.com\" target=\"_blank\">SPARK Architects</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t这些漂浮在水面的仿佛小吃一条街似的建筑是 SPARK 工作室为新加坡设计的漂浮集市，可以在全球各个城市的静态水面为人们提供享受美食和社交的场所。这些建筑依靠太阳能自给自足，可移动并重新组合以适应不同的水面。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220610Q9vZWGSu3nlzkgqw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.553125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220611DksIYjwy1AvHldCG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220611Ld82yD6Q9uVUnYbq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t3.  LaMetric by <a href=\"smartatoms.com\" target=\"_blank\">Smart Atoms</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t邮件、日程、天气、Facebook、结婚纪念日、股票、Paypal 收款⋯⋯一切新消息都需要去不同的网站或者 APP 里查询的日子终于结束了，英国公司 Smart Atoms 推出的LeMetric 相当于一款智能闹钟，通过 app 集合智能手机里你需要的功能，一切推送通知都会显示在这个复古风格的屏幕上，保证你不会错过任何重要的事情。<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/smartatoms/lametric-customizable-smart-ticker-for-life-and-bu\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里预订</a>。\r\n<embed src=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNzMxMTM0MTQ0/v.swf\" quality=\"high\" width=\"640\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\"></embed>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220611D0ukjUe1HnWo7ViB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052206129WE4L5IBFTo0GyzZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.35625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220613j9oGTlEJLgF7AsKv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3953125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220613fldT1vXmrSqcgwth.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052206144rhkntqvIfBlpY9J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220614fbqplv5Mgx68w7XP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">4.  Jar RGB lighting for Lasvit by </span><a href=\"www.ariklevy.fr\" target=\"_blank\">Arik Levy</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t这组灯具运用了薄彩色玻璃吹制技术，灵感来自 RGB 的色彩混合概念。像一支支悬挂在一起的酒瓶，光线透过来都能变得清脆起来。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052206151RP4HzQba5EAVYJZ.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220615r8zIwmyMGL103DeU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220616VsWnU1KalFAcqvp9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t5.  Chain-embellished felt cap by <a href=\"http://www.lanvin.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Lanvin</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t这款链饰毡帽来自 Lanvin 2014 早秋系列。帽子是这一系列的核心主题，这款毡帽正面有金色细链装饰，造型相当挺括，戴着它简直就是把“多金有品“四个大字顶在头上，但是不要觉得这是鸭舌帽就可以搭嘻哈风。<a href=\"http://www.net-a-porter.com/product/452741/Lanvin/chain-embellished-felt-cap\" target=\"_blank\">点击购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220616ZbKQRNa6o2p0nlAw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}